@baseUrl = http://192.168.43.251:8080

### 获取商品列表
GET {{baseUrl}}/products

### 创建订单
POST {{baseUrl}}/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "payment_method": "wechat",
  "items": [
    {
      "products_id": 22,
      "quantity": 2
    },
    {
      "products_id": 22,
      "quantity": 10
    }
  ]
}


### 测试修改后的假逻辑
### =========================================
### 商品模块 (Products) - 软删除测试验证
### =========================================

### 1. 先获取当前所有商品，找一个你想删除的商品 ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/products

### 2. 执行软删除 (假设你要删除 ID 为 1 的商品，请替换为你数据库里真实存在的 ID)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/products?id=25

### 3. 再次获取商品列表，验证该商品是否已经从结果中消失
GET {{baseUrl}}/products

### 2. 创建订单 (测试传入不存在的商品ID)
POST {{baseUrl}}/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "payment_method": "alipay",
  "items": [
    {
      "products_id": 9999, 
      "quantity": 1
    }
  ]
}
### 3. 扭转订单状态 (接单制作)
PATCH http://localhost:8080/orders/1/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "processing"
}

### 4. 扭转订单状态 (完成订单)
PATCH http://localhost:8080/orders/1/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "completed"
}

### 5. 扭转订单状态 (测试非法状态)
PATCH http://localhost:8080/orders/1/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "hahaha" 
}
### 6. 创建商品 (测试 multipart/form-data)
POST {{baseUrl}}/products
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

name=极客招牌汉堡&price=28.5&stock=5&is_active=true

#### 7. 获取商品列表，验证新商品是否成功创建
GET {{baseUrl}}/products

### 8. 创建订单 (测试正常流程)
POST {{baseUrl}}/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "payment_method": "wechat",
  "items": [
    {
      "products_id": 30, 
      "quantity": 2
    }
  ]
}

### 9. 创建订单 (测试库存不足)
POST {{baseUrl}}/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "payment_method": "alipay",
  "items": [
    {
      "products_id": 30, 
      "quantity": 3
    }
  ]
}

### 8. 老板手动强行上架测试 (无库存状态下)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/products/30/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "is_active": true
}

### 测试用例 1：【正常购买】标准的黄金链路
# 预期结果：返回 200 OK，包含 order_id、order_no 和正确的 total_amount。
# 验证点：去数据库检查 orders 表总价是否正确，order_items 是否写入，products 表对应的商品库存是否正确扣减！
POST {{baseUrl}}/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "payment_method": "wechat_pay",
  "items": [
    {
      "products_id": 22, 
      "quantity": 2
    },
    {
      "products_id": 13,
      "quantity": 1
    }
  ]
}

### 测试用例 2：【防御测试】防超卖与库存不足拦截
# 假设商品 ID 为 22 的库存只有 10 件。
# 预期结果：返回 400 Bad Request。
# 验证点：系统必须优雅地抛出错误 {"success": false, "error": "Exception: 商品 [...] 库存不足"}，且数据库库存【绝对不能】变成负数。
POST {{baseUrl}}/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "payment_method": "cash",
  "items": [
    {
      "products_id": 22, 
      "quantity": 9999 
    }
  ]
}

### 测试用例 3：【边界测试】空订单/脏数据拦截
# 预期结果：返回 400 Bad Request。
# 验证点：系统必须拦截没有 items 的请求，绝不能在数据库里生成金额为 0 的幽灵订单。
POST {{baseUrl}}/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "payment_method": "cash",
  "items": []
}

### =========================================
### MDM 模块 (Devices) - 设备管理与心跳
### =========================================

### 1. 设备列表
GET {{baseUrl}}/devices

### 2. 设备详情
GET {{baseUrl}}/devices/POS001

### 3. 心跳上报 (移除电量，添加位置)
POST {{baseUrl}}/devices/POS001/heartbeat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "storage_usage": 45.2,
  "memory_usage": 62.1,
  "network_type": "wifi",
  "signal_strength": -65,
  "app_version": "1.0.0",
  "latitude": 22.5431,
  "longitude": 114.0579
}

### 4. 设备轮询 (获取待执行命令)
GET {{baseUrl}}/devices/POS001/heartbeat

### 5. 下发远程命令
POST {{baseUrl}}/devices/POS001/commands
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "command": "lock_screen",
  "params": {}
}

### 6. 查询命令状态
GET {{baseUrl}}/devices/POS001/commands

### 7. 命令确认
POST {{baseUrl}}/devices/POS001/commands/1/ack
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "completed"
}

### 8. 批量下发命令
POST {{baseUrl}}/devices/batch-commands
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "device_ids": ["POS001", "POS002"],
  "command": "reboot",
  "params": {"message": "设备将在5分钟后重启"}
}

### 9. 修改设备状态
PUT {{baseUrl}}/devices/POS001
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "suspended"
}

### 10. 解绑设备
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/devices/POS001